          <text><![CDATA[<p><b>Helping to End Addiction and Lessen Substance Use Disorders Act of 2018 or the HEAL Act of 2018</b></p> <p>This bill establishes a series of requirements under Medicare and Medicaid relating to substance-use disorder prevention and treatment, including educational programs, screening requirements, and prescription drug monitoring. </p>]]></text>
